result.name: Congee and Noodle Shop

reviews.text:
Always good. Always noisy and crowded at lunch hours. But you can't resist coming back again and again every so often.

Rice (with various kind of  meat) in clay pot is good for winter time. A little bit on the salty side though.

Nice quality of congee and side dishes. But staff and cashier are enjoyed chitchat at the dining hall while there were only one customer was dining. Definitely the morale amongst the staff is excellent but could that be a bit more professional when there are customer?
Generous portion of noodles but i'm not impressed with the taste. May have ordered the wrong dish (i.e. dry wanton noodles with vegetables)

I went this restaurant at dinner time. It was calm and all foods were delicious. Taste wasn’t unique but it was okay, not salty not too much greasy and reasonable price. I’m satisfied with my dinner here.
clean, good value for money

result.name: 粥麵館

reviews.text:
粥麵館係米之蓮推介嘅舖頭之一，今日又有機會喺度食午餐。由於我於一年多前喺度食過粥，所以今日一於試吓佢嘅煲仔蒸飯

香菇滑雞煲仔蒸飯，餸菜鋪滿成個飯面，冬菇好香好入味，雞件大大件又好滑。
食煲仔飯或者蒸飯又點少得煲仔飯豉油呢？舖頭好細心，鼓油係另上的，用碗仔裝起，豉油份量由你自己添加同控制。
煲仔飯中的飯是放係砂煲中煮熟的，並不是一般那樣將煮好飯菜放進去，而且味道確實很好👍🏻
金針雲耳生魚片煲仔飯必食，生滾粥好味，食滿三百元可以免費泊車，22元一小時。
光顧多年，不是常客，但水準穩定，出品不俗。個人推薦涼瓜排骨粥，炸醬麵，豬膶粥。

Always good. Always noisy and crowded at lunch hours. But you can't resist coming back again and again every so often.

Rice (with various kind of  meat) in clay pot is good for winter time. A little bit on the salty side though.
環境舒適但較嘈，食物俾足料，味道鮮美。茶餐廳價錢，傳統味道，非一般粥粉麵飯。讚！

result.name: Foo Ka Chinese Restaurant

reviews.text: The food, the decor and the service are good. The price is reasonable. Very conveniently located. It is not far from Quarry Bay C exit and also well serviced by a number of bus lines and trams.

Good place for dinner.
Steamed rice in clay casserole was very good if provided with lard!
Tangerine peel spare ribs and eel were good.

Nice dim sum, spacious, excellent view of the harbour and reasonably priced. It's not  located at any shopping mall, though, and some may find its being next to Hong Kong's best known funeral home a little unsettling. But it's definitely one of my favorite Chinese restaurants.

One of the best Cantonese restaurant in the area.
Great service and delicious dishes.
Great for driving with wheelchair access lift.
Usually quite in the weekend, and a hot spot during weekdays.
Service ~ good; with quality food

result.name: 富嘉閣

reviews.text: 環境寬敞,乾淨,坐位不太密集,服務好,一口吃進去的點心沒太鮮味證明沒有太多味精,所以吃來感覺可口,炸物是即叫即炸出來非常脆挺,比起灣仔陶源酒樓的炸物又油又膩優勝很多
粵式點心與小菜均佳，較難訂到座位。
The food, the decor and the service are good. The price is reasonable. Very conveniently located. It is not far from Quarry Bay C exit and also well serviced by a number of bus lines and trams.

Good place for dinner.
Steamed rice in clay casserole was very good if provided with lard!
Tangerine peel spare ribs and eel were good.
